Lately, I've started muscle training. Along with the development
of my biceps, I feel like I've become more positive. Indeed, our
body is our capital in everything, huh...

Actually, I'm from this place, you know. Oh, returning to my
hometown after a long time... Oh my, it's so boring. I want to
hurry up and go back to Yurisine.
\SE[2]Here it is... \SE[3]I wonder if everything is ready...?
